00:00:17.317 --> 00:00:20.522 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Breathing heavily ]

00:00:20.555 --> 00:00:27.929 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:00:27.962 --> 00:00:29.664 position:38% line:89% align:start
Finally.

00:00:29.697 --> 00:00:34.034 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:00:34.067 --> 00:00:36.871 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Sighs ]

00:00:36.905 --> 00:00:39.541 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's finally over.

00:00:39.574 --> 00:00:43.210 position:19% line:89% align:start
Headon: No. [ Scoffs ]

00:00:43.243 --> 00:00:45.880 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's just the beginning.

00:00:45.914 --> 00:00:54.288 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:00:54.321 --> 00:00:56.658 position:19% line:89% align:start
Rachel: I'm sorry, Bam.

00:00:56.691 --> 00:00:58.560 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:00:58.593 --> 00:01:00.762 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Breathing rapidly ]

00:01:00.795 --> 00:01:02.964 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:01:02.997 --> 00:01:06.099 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's calling me.

00:01:06.133 --> 00:01:08.703 position:38% line:83% align:start
You know
I have to climb the tower.

00:01:08.736 --> 00:01:11.673 position:27% line:89% align:start
Forget about me.

00:01:11.706 --> 00:01:14.576 position:27% line:89% align:start
The tower, it...

00:01:14.609 --> 00:01:16.310 position:27% line:89% align:start
it's calling me.

00:01:16.343 --> 00:01:20.715 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:20.748 --> 00:01:22.316 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:01:22.349 --> 00:01:27.120 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:27.154 --> 00:01:29.356 position:16% line:5% align:start
This will probably be...

00:01:29.389 --> 00:01:32.827 position:16% line:83% align:start
the moment all my dreams
come true.

00:01:34.294 --> 00:01:37.397 position:41% line:83% align:start
Headon:
Oh, no, it wasn't you.

00:01:37.431 --> 00:01:38.600 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:01:38.633 --> 00:01:42.570 position:27% line:77% align:start
Indeed, the tower
wasn't calling you.

00:01:43.905 --> 00:01:45.840 position:55% line:89% align:start
But I...

00:01:45.873 --> 00:01:50.011 position:41% line:5% align:start
No, I -- I beg you,
let me in.

00:01:50.044 --> 00:01:52.013 position:41% line:5% align:start
Please, let me in.

00:01:52.046 --> 00:01:54.481 position:44% line:5% align:start
Give me a chance.

00:01:54.515 --> 00:01:55.817 position:21% line:89% align:start
A chance?

00:01:55.850 --> 00:01:59.152 position:27% line:83% align:start
You must. I've dreamt of
climbing the tower for so long.

00:01:59.186 --> 00:02:01.455 position:47% line:89% align:start
Please, please!

00:02:02.657 --> 00:02:05.359 position:5% line:89% align:start
Then let us test you.

00:02:05.392 --> 00:02:06.360 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:02:06.393 --> 00:02:10.031 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:10.064 --> 00:02:11.264 position:44% line:89% align:start
What do you mean?

00:02:11.298 --> 00:02:14.434 position:5% line:89% align:start
The rules are simple.

00:02:14.468 --> 00:02:18.405 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>He was merciless, hurling</i>
 <i>nothing but despair my way.</i>

00:02:18.438 --> 00:02:22.110 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>Everything was supposed to be</i>
 <i>mine once I climbed the tower.</i>

00:02:22.142 --> 00:02:25.046 position:30% line:83% align:start
I can't pass this test.
I'll fail.

00:02:25.079 --> 00:02:26.814 position:44% line:83% align:start
How can I take on
that monster?

00:02:26.848 --> 00:02:29.550 position:21% line:83% align:start
I don't even have a weapon
to protect myself.

00:02:29.584 --> 00:02:32.152 position:38% line:83% align:start
It's cruel to assign
such an impossible task!

00:02:32.185 --> 00:02:33.621 position:21% line:89% align:start
Silence.

00:02:33.655 --> 00:02:35.322 position:44% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps, groans ]

00:02:35.355 --> 00:02:38.059 position:7% line:83% align:start
Now open your eyes
and watch...

00:02:38.092 --> 00:02:39.459 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:02:39.493 --> 00:02:43.064 position:5% line:83% align:start
...as your true savior
is revealed.

00:02:43.097 --> 00:02:48.468 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:48.503 --> 00:02:50.203 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:02:50.237 --> 00:02:52.073 position:24% line:89% align:start
This is too much to bear.

00:02:52.106 --> 00:02:55.910 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:55.943 --> 00:02:58.579 position:44% line:89% align:start
My savior is Bam?

00:02:59.781 --> 00:03:03.450 position:41% line:83% align:start
But all he ever did
was follow me around.

00:03:03.483 --> 00:03:07.088 position:61% line:83% align:start
Why?
Why does he get everything?

00:03:07.121 --> 00:03:08.790 position:47% line:89% align:start
He's just Bam.

00:03:08.823 --> 00:03:13.628 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:03:13.661 --> 00:03:17.497 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm quite interested in watching
what will happen next.

00:03:17.532 --> 00:03:20.935 position:5% line:83% align:start
Not that you'll be there
to see it, of course.

00:03:22.837 --> 00:03:24.237 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Grunts ]

00:03:24.271 --> 00:03:27.108 position:5% line:83% align:start
Do you understand now
why you weren't chosen

00:03:27.141 --> 00:03:29.376 position:7% line:89% align:start
to climb the tower?

00:03:29.409 --> 00:03:33.181 position:5% line:83% align:start
Pathetic. That was hardly
any Shinsu at all.

00:03:33.213 --> 00:03:34.716 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're too weak.

00:03:34.749 --> 00:03:38.251 position:7% line:83% align:start
There's an ugliness
that seeps out from inside you.

00:03:38.285 --> 00:03:42.190 position:13% line:83% align:start
You don't have
an ounce of charm about you.

00:03:42.222 --> 00:03:44.257 position:44% line:5% align:start
Say what you like
about me.

00:03:44.291 --> 00:03:46.961 position:44% line:5% align:start
But I desperately
want to see the stars.

00:03:46.994 --> 00:03:48.395 position:30% line:89% align:start
No.

00:03:48.428 --> 00:03:50.865 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's clear you want to
 <i>become</i> a star.

00:03:50.898 --> 00:03:52.466 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:03:52.499 --> 00:03:54.502 position:5% line:83% align:start
Don't you want to shine
the brightest?

00:03:54.535 --> 00:03:57.138 position:13% line:83% align:start
To be special?
Be admired?

00:03:57.171 --> 00:04:00.842 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:00.875 --> 00:04:02.375 position:30% line:5% align:start
Please let me climb it.

00:04:02.409 --> 00:04:06.446 position:21% line:5% align:start
I have to climb the tower.
I'll do anything you ask.

00:04:07.915 --> 00:04:09.382 position:21% line:89% align:start
Anything?

00:04:09.416 --> 00:04:12.153 position:44% line:5% align:start
Anything at all.

00:04:12.186 --> 00:04:13.821 position:50% line:89% align:start
Just name it.

00:04:13.855 --> 00:04:16.256 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:16.289 --> 00:04:19.026 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then, out of respect
for your bottomless stupidity

00:04:19.060 --> 00:04:20.695 position:5% line:89% align:start
and self-serving nature,

00:04:20.728 --> 00:04:23.564 position:13% line:83% align:start
let us conduct
a special test.

00:04:23.598 --> 00:04:24.966 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:24.999 --> 00:04:26.667 position:44% line:89% align:start
What's the test?

00:04:29.704 --> 00:04:32.807 position:10% line:83% align:start
If you can manage
to bring his life to a close,

00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:36.577 position:5% line:83% align:start
I will grant you permission
to climb the tower.

00:04:36.611 --> 00:04:37.444 position:61% line:5% align:start
What?

00:04:37.477 --> 00:04:39.781 position:5% line:89% align:start
You must end Bam's story

00:04:39.814 --> 00:04:41.314 position:5% line:89% align:start
with your own hands,

00:04:41.348 --> 00:04:42.650 position:13% line:89% align:start
no one else's.

00:04:42.683 --> 00:04:45.553 position:35% line:83% align:start
Your condition is you
want me to kill Bam?

00:04:45.586 --> 00:04:47.688 position:10% line:83% align:start
Why do you sound
so surprised?

00:04:47.722 --> 00:04:51.291 position:5% line:83% align:start
You don't need him anymore.
You abandoned him.

00:04:51.324 --> 00:04:53.293 position:19% line:5% align:start
Remember?
That's not what I...

00:04:53.326 --> 00:04:56.964 position:7% line:83% align:start
Only you can decide
what happens now.

00:04:59.967 --> 00:05:01.702 position:44% line:83% align:start
I'm going to need
a weapon.

00:05:01.736 --> 00:05:03.470 position:58% line:83% align:start
Bam has
an incredible weapon.

00:05:03.504 --> 00:05:05.206 position:58% line:83% align:start
Come on.
[ Chuckles ]

00:05:05.239 --> 00:05:06.707 position:5% line:89% align:start
You're steadfast dedication

00:05:06.741 --> 00:05:09.977 position:5% line:83% align:start
to your own self-interest
is impressive.

00:05:12.046 --> 00:05:16.751 position:5% line:83% align:start
Consider him your bodyguard,
your gatekeeper to hell.

00:05:16.784 --> 00:05:20.588 position:21% line:83% align:start
Just once
you will be resurrected.

00:05:22.256 --> 00:05:25.960 position:5% line:83% align:start
Woman: It's okay to kill all
of them, right?

00:05:25.993 --> 00:05:28.495 position:30% line:89% align:start
Rachel: Yes, of course,

00:05:28.529 --> 00:05:31.098 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>I sincerely wished...</i>

00:05:31.132 --> 00:05:33.366 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>for someone else to kill Bam.</i>

00:05:33.400 --> 00:05:35.636 position:41% line:89% align:start
Please don't worry.

00:05:35.670 --> 00:05:38.639 position:24% line:89% align:start
We won't steal the crown.

00:05:38.673 --> 00:05:40.041 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>After all,</i>

00:05:40.074 --> 00:05:43.611 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I could never kill Bam...</i>
 <i>even for the tower.</i>

00:05:43.644 --> 00:05:50.117 position:10% line:71% align:start
Observe him?
Yes, to see if the boy
is worthy of what we desire.

00:05:50.151 --> 00:05:52.753 position:41% line:83% align:start
The girl will serve
as the bait.

00:05:53.754 --> 00:05:56.924 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:05:56.958 --> 00:06:01.996 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is wrong. I mean, wasn't</i>
 <i>he supposed to die for me?</i>

00:06:02.029 --> 00:06:04.799 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:06:04.832 --> 00:06:07.001 position:30% line:89% align:start
Bam: No! Don't!

00:06:07.034 --> 00:06:10.538 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:06:10.571 --> 00:06:13.941 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Why? Why would you save me?</i>

00:06:13.975 --> 00:06:15.776 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>You shouldn't have.</i>

00:06:15.810 --> 00:06:20.681 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>After all,</i>
 <i>I'm supposed to kill you.</i>

00:06:20.715 --> 00:06:23.751 position:5% line:83% align:start
Khun: You want me to lie to him?
Say you're not Rachel?

00:06:23.784 --> 00:06:27.387 position:66% line:71% align:start
Yes.
I can't let him
look at me anymore.

00:06:27.420 --> 00:06:29.857 position:7% line:83% align:start
You know, Bam wants
to be with you, right?

00:06:29.891 --> 00:06:31.626 position:35% line:89% align:start
We can't be together.

00:06:31.659 --> 00:06:35.129 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'd lay low</i>
 <i>and wait for my chance.</i>

00:06:35.162 --> 00:06:36.831 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>At least that was the plan.</i>

00:06:36.864 --> 00:06:40.134 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>But my body refused</i>
 <i>to listen to me.</i>

00:06:40.167 --> 00:06:42.770 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Time continued to pass.</i>

00:06:42.803 --> 00:06:44.572 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:06:44.605 --> 00:06:46.107 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Before I knew it,</i>

00:06:46.140 --> 00:06:50.711 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I hoarded points,</i>
 <i>terrified of spending any.</i>

00:06:50.745 --> 00:06:52.947 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>What if I can't kill a Bam?</i>

00:06:52.980 --> 00:06:58.286 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I can't climb the tower,</i>
 <i>not with this few points.</i>

00:06:58.319 --> 00:07:01.656 position:44% line:89% align:start
 <i>Why?</i>

00:07:01.689 --> 00:07:05.826 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>He keeps getting</i>
 <i>everything I want.</i>

00:07:05.860 --> 00:07:08.729 position:10% line:83% align:start
I hope whatever you're seeking
at the top of the tower

00:07:08.763 --> 00:07:11.799 position:50% line:83% align:start
is worth more
than losing him.

00:07:11.832 --> 00:07:15.336 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:15.369 --> 00:07:17.171 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's the same thing.</i>

00:07:17.204 --> 00:07:19.540 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Always "Bam, Bam, Bam."</i>

00:07:19.573 --> 00:07:21.175 position:24% line:89% align:start
What does she know?

00:07:21.208 --> 00:07:26.547 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:26.580 --> 00:07:28.950 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>But can I do it?</i>

00:07:28.983 --> 00:07:31.419 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can't, can I?</i>

00:07:32.853 --> 00:07:35.690 position:21% line:83% align:start
At this rate, you'll never
climb the tower.

00:07:35.723 --> 00:07:37.591 position:41% line:83% align:start
Or have you already
given up hope?

00:07:37.625 --> 00:07:39.260 position:5% line:89% align:start
Of course I haven't!

00:07:39.293 --> 00:07:42.029 position:19% line:83% align:start
Then make use of everything
you have at your disposal.

00:07:42.063 --> 00:07:46.033 position:10% line:71% align:start
Huh?
Go along with the disturbance
that's about to occur.

00:07:46.067 --> 00:07:49.637 position:16% line:83% align:start
Create a situation that will
allow you to stick close to Bam

00:07:49.670 --> 00:07:51.372 position:35% line:89% align:start
during the next test.

00:07:51.405 --> 00:07:52.974 position:19% line:89% align:start
Create...?

00:07:53.007 --> 00:07:54.608 position:5% line:89% align:start
What am I supposed to do?

00:07:54.642 --> 00:07:56.911 position:41% line:83% align:start
When the time comes
to choose,

00:07:56.944 --> 00:07:58.646 position:38% line:89% align:start
you'll understand...

00:07:58.679 --> 00:08:01.716 position:38% line:83% align:start
as long as you don't
misread the signs.

00:08:01.749 --> 00:08:03.884 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm here because
I'd like to chat.

00:08:03.918 --> 00:08:06.320 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'd like to talk
to you about Bam.

00:08:06.354 --> 00:08:08.689 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Don't misread the signs?</i>

00:08:11.692 --> 00:08:14.662 position:19% line:83% align:start
It said if I got rid of you
Bam would go too.

00:08:14.695 --> 00:08:16.764 position:16% line:77% align:start
[ Gasps ]
 <i>I'll do anything.</i>

00:08:16.797 --> 00:08:19.100 position:27% line:83% align:start
Whatever it takes
to climb the tower.

00:08:19.133 --> 00:08:20.634 position:52% line:89% align:start
Hoh, stop.

00:08:20.668 --> 00:08:22.370 position:41% line:89% align:start
What are you doing?

00:08:22.403 --> 00:08:23.804 position:5% line:89% align:start
All of it is your fault!

00:08:23.838 --> 00:08:25.973 position:5% line:83% align:start
You shouldn't have shown
off your power!

00:08:26.007 --> 00:08:27.274 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:08:27.308 --> 00:08:30.044 position:35% line:83% align:start
Let me go!
-[ Grunts ] Stop it!

00:08:30.077 --> 00:08:32.146 position:61% line:77% align:start
[ Gasps ]
 <i>Did I make the right choice?</i>

00:08:32.179 --> 00:08:33.547 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Exhales sharply ]

00:08:33.581 --> 00:08:35.483 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>It didn't hurt at all.</i>

00:08:35.516 --> 00:08:37.551 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>I have a backup.</i>

00:08:37.585 --> 00:08:40.521 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-No! Rachel!

00:08:40.554 --> 00:08:42.089 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Is this what she meant?</i>

00:08:42.123 --> 00:08:45.159 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Creating a situation</i>
 <i>that lets me stick by him?</i>

00:08:45.192 --> 00:08:47.561 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Rachel!
 <i>-Is this right now?</i>

00:08:47.595 --> 00:08:50.164 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Now I can climb the tower.</i>

00:08:50.197 --> 00:08:52.099 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Now I can...</i>

00:08:52.133 --> 00:08:54.035 position:44% line:89% align:start
 <i>Bam.</i>

00:08:54.068 --> 00:08:55.536 position:58% line:89% align:start
Rachel!

00:08:55.569 --> 00:08:58.239 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Sweet, kind-hearted Bam.</i>

00:08:58.272 --> 00:09:00.307 position:27% line:89% align:start
Rachel, wake up, please!

00:09:00.341 --> 00:09:01.842 position:24% line:89% align:start
Bam...

00:09:01.876 --> 00:09:05.046 position:19% line:83% align:start
why did...
you follow me?

00:09:05.079 --> 00:09:08.049 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:09:08.082 --> 00:09:10.284 position:5% line:89% align:start
I told you not to come.

00:09:10.317 --> 00:09:12.521 position:27% line:83% align:start
I...
[ Gasps ]

00:09:12.553 --> 00:09:14.588 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>After that, it was amusing</i>

00:09:14.622 --> 00:09:16.457 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>how much everything</i>
 <i>went according to plan,</i>

00:09:16.490 --> 00:09:18.592 position:10% line:89% align:start
My legs can be Rachel's legs.

00:09:18.626 --> 00:09:20.261 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can take her up
the tower myself.

00:09:20.294 --> 00:09:21.862 position:16% line:89% align:start
What the...?

00:09:21.896 --> 00:09:24.598 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>As long as I did</i>
 <i>what she said...</i>

00:09:24.632 --> 00:09:27.168 position:38% line:83% align:start
May I offer a prayer
as well?

00:09:27.201 --> 00:09:28.836 position:24% line:89% align:start
Of course you can.

00:09:28.869 --> 00:09:33.340 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>...the chance to kill him</i>
 <i>would come soon enough.</i>

00:09:33.374 --> 00:09:35.709 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I just had to wait for it.</i>

00:09:35.743 --> 00:09:38.412 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>It was that simple.</i>

00:09:38.446 --> 00:09:40.414 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Thank you.
-Huh?

00:09:40.448 --> 00:09:43.584 position:41% line:83% align:start
I'm glad you could
attend Hoh's funeral.

00:09:43.617 --> 00:09:45.286 position:33% line:89% align:start
I know that it's hard.

00:09:45.319 --> 00:09:46.754 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>My mind's made up.</i>

00:09:46.787 --> 00:09:49.190 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'd give up everything</i>
 <i>to achieve my dream.</i>

00:09:49.223 --> 00:09:50.357 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>I've decided.</i>

00:09:50.391 --> 00:09:52.326 position:50% line:89% align:start
Hey, Rachel.

00:09:54.195 --> 00:09:56.330 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Sobbing ]

00:09:56.363 --> 00:09:59.100 position:41% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry. I upset.
Or...

00:09:59.133 --> 00:10:00.701 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Run, Bam.</i>

00:10:00.734 --> 00:10:04.573 position:10% line:5% align:start
Why are you here?
I abandoned you.
 <i>Run.</i>

00:10:04.605 --> 00:10:07.975 position:5% line:71% align:start
I was desperate
to see the stars.
 <i>Run.</i>

00:10:08.008 --> 00:10:09.743 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Run! Run!</i>

00:10:09.777 --> 00:10:13.314 position:21% line:83% align:start
Run! Run!
Run! Run! Run!

00:10:13.347 --> 00:10:14.982 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please.

00:10:15.015 --> 00:10:16.518 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:16.551 --> 00:10:19.787 position:7% line:83% align:start
So, I guess that...
now...

00:10:19.820 --> 00:10:22.356 position:13% line:83% align:start
it's your turn
to abandon me.

00:10:22.389 --> 00:10:24.391 position:7% line:89% align:start
Or I really will...

00:10:24.425 --> 00:10:26.060 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:26.093 --> 00:10:30.264 position:5% line:83% align:start
After what happened,
you don't need me anymore.

00:10:30.297 --> 00:10:33.801 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:33.834 --> 00:10:36.003 position:30% line:89% align:start
A shining ray of light.

00:10:36.036 --> 00:10:37.071 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:37.104 --> 00:10:40.474 position:52% line:83% align:start
You lit up
my dark and lonely world.

00:10:40.509 --> 00:10:43.377 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:43.410 --> 00:10:45.514 position:27% line:89% align:start
You showed me the light.

00:10:45.547 --> 00:10:47.248 position:50% line:89% align:start
I'm so lucky.

00:10:49.584 --> 00:10:51.520 position:44% line:83% align:start
No one could ever
replace you.

00:10:51.553 --> 00:10:52.887 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:10:52.920 --> 00:10:55.557 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:55.590 --> 00:10:59.827 position:5% line:83% align:start
[ Crying ] I'm sorry.
I'm so sorry, Bam.

00:10:59.860 --> 00:11:02.296 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm -- I'm not a light.</i>

00:11:02.329 --> 00:11:05.099 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm too black and muddy.</i>

00:11:05.132 --> 00:11:07.801 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Your words touched</i>
 <i>nothing in me.</i>

00:11:07.835 --> 00:11:09.970 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>They fell on deaf ears.</i>

00:11:10.004 --> 00:11:12.541 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>The tower is everything to me.</i>

00:11:12.574 --> 00:11:13.941 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I was so jealous of you.</i>

00:11:13.974 --> 00:11:16.443 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>It drove me to my madness.</i>

00:11:16.477 --> 00:11:18.547 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>I hated you.</i>

00:11:18.580 --> 00:11:20.447 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>But my heart's unsure...</i>

00:11:20.481 --> 00:11:22.416 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>and they won't be</i>

00:11:22.449 --> 00:11:24.586 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>so forgiving</i>
 <i>of my uncertainty.</i>

00:11:24.619 --> 00:11:26.854 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do you know
what you desire?

00:11:26.887 --> 00:11:28.989 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-This is your last chance.

00:11:29.023 --> 00:11:33.160 position:5% line:83% align:start
The last opportunity you'll have
to reach the top of the tower.

00:11:33.194 --> 00:11:35.729 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:11:35.763 --> 00:11:39.466 position:5% line:83% align:start
Well, Rachel, consider yourself
extremely fortunate.

00:11:39.500 --> 00:11:41.570 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>There's nowhere to run now.</i>

00:11:41.603 --> 00:11:43.804 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>I have to do it.</i>

00:11:43.837 --> 00:11:45.339 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's going to be okay.

00:11:45.372 --> 00:11:48.209 position:50% line:83% align:start
Our teammates
are strong, smart and capable.

00:11:48.242 --> 00:11:51.078 position:41% line:89% align:start
They'll protect us.

00:11:51.111 --> 00:11:53.247 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're right.

00:11:53.280 --> 00:11:56.350 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did you ever imagine
something like this?

00:11:56.383 --> 00:12:00.888 position:66% line:71% align:start
What?
Back we stared
at the roof of the cave.

00:12:00.921 --> 00:12:04.458 position:30% line:83% align:start
Did you imagine
we'd end up here?

00:12:04.491 --> 00:12:06.628 position:58% line:89% align:start
I did.

00:12:06.661 --> 00:12:08.862 position:58% line:83% align:start
Even in
the future I dreamt,

00:12:08.896 --> 00:12:12.032 position:35% line:83% align:start
I always knew someday
I'd end up here with you.

00:12:12.066 --> 00:12:15.202 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Maybe there's a way for me</i>
 <i>to climb the tower with Bam.</i>

00:12:18.005 --> 00:12:20.741 position:27% line:83% align:start
You're not afraid
in the slightest, Bam, are you?

00:12:20.774 --> 00:12:23.043 position:27% line:83% align:start
I am,
but if I acted scared,

00:12:23.077 --> 00:12:26.615 position:16% line:71% align:start
wouldn't that
just make you anxious?
[ Exhales ]

00:12:26.648 --> 00:12:28.782 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Laughs ]

00:12:28.816 --> 00:12:32.621 position:5% line:89% align:start
Rachel? What's wrong?

00:12:32.654 --> 00:12:34.788 position:41% line:83% align:start
Look at you acting
all cool and heroic.

00:12:34.822 --> 00:12:35.923 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Chuckles ]

00:12:35.956 --> 00:12:37.891 position:5% line:5% align:start
Just like old times.

00:12:37.925 --> 00:12:39.793 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>You look at me so intently</i>

00:12:39.827 --> 00:12:41.428 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>with those sweet eyes.</i>

00:12:41.462 --> 00:12:44.865 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>You're the only one</i>
 <i>who treats me like I'm special.</i>

00:12:44.898 --> 00:12:47.935 position:5% line:83% align:start
What is it that you truly desire
from the tower?

00:12:47.968 --> 00:12:51.939 position:64% line:71% align:start
Huh?
It's clear you want
to become a star.

00:12:51.972 --> 00:12:53.907 position:5% line:83% align:start
Don't you want to shine
the brightest?

00:12:53.941 --> 00:12:56.277 position:13% line:83% align:start
To be special?
Be admired?

00:12:56.310 --> 00:12:58.445 position:5% line:83% align:start
The Guardian asked me
what I wanted --

00:12:58.479 --> 00:13:01.549 position:5% line:83% align:start
what I wanted when I finally got
to the top of the tower.

00:13:01.583 --> 00:13:03.050 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:03.083 --> 00:13:05.419 position:7% line:83% align:start
And the first thing
that immediately came to mind

00:13:05.452 --> 00:13:06.954 position:13% line:89% align:start
was your face.

00:13:06.987 --> 00:13:11.125 position:5% line:83% align:start
The thing I saw after that
was the cafeteria.

00:13:12.393 --> 00:13:15.329 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's when it finally</i>
 <i>sunk in for me.</i>

00:13:17.666 --> 00:13:20.301 position:47% line:83% align:start
You're amazing,
you know that?

00:13:20.334 --> 00:13:25.674 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>No, I knew all along</i>
 <i>but wouldn't acknowledge it.</i>

00:13:25.707 --> 00:13:26.840 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hey.

00:13:26.874 --> 00:13:30.077 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>He became the star,</i>
 <i>not me.</i>

00:13:30.110 --> 00:13:32.647 position:58% line:83% align:start
Rachel,
you feel it too, right?

00:13:32.681 --> 00:13:35.382 position:19% line:89% align:start
Huh? Yeah.

00:13:35.416 --> 00:13:37.084 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:13:37.117 --> 00:13:39.219 position:55% line:83% align:start
I wonder
what this light is.

00:13:39.253 --> 00:13:42.856 position:19% line:83% align:start
It feels like there's power
welling up inside of me.

00:13:42.890 --> 00:13:46.260 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Bam has so many things</i>
 <i>I don't have.</i>

00:13:46.293 --> 00:13:50.264 position:7% line:83% align:start
-Anything is possible in here.
-Huh?

00:13:50.297 --> 00:13:54.335 position:7% line:83% align:start
I mean, after all,
we're inside Shinsu right now,

00:13:54.368 --> 00:13:57.838 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll never experience</i>
 <i>the miracle of Shinsu.</i>

00:13:57.871 --> 00:13:59.440 position:30% line:83% align:start
Bam is the one
who's special.

00:13:59.473 --> 00:14:01.875 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, no, it wasn't you.

00:14:01.909 --> 00:14:03.977 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm just supplemental.</i>

00:14:04.011 --> 00:14:06.280 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>The moon borrowing</i>
 <i>the sun's light.</i>

00:14:06.313 --> 00:14:09.718 position:27% line:71% align:start
Everything's going to be
okay, Rachel.
Huh?

00:14:09.751 --> 00:14:11.919 position:33% line:83% align:start
No matter what happens
from now on,

00:14:11.952 --> 00:14:13.822 position:47% line:83% align:start
there's nothing
to worry about.

00:14:13.854 --> 00:14:15.389 position:50% line:83% align:start
I'll take you
to the top.

00:14:15.422 --> 00:14:18.693 position:35% line:77% align:start
We'll climb the tower
together.
[ Exhales ]

00:14:18.727 --> 00:14:22.096 position:21% line:77% align:start
Bam.
 <i>If I stay with you, then I...</i>

00:14:22.129 --> 00:14:23.864 position:61% line:83% align:start
Also,
I'm a different person

00:14:23.897 --> 00:14:25.499 position:50% line:83% align:start
from the one
back in that cave.

00:14:25.533 --> 00:14:27.468 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>...I can't become a star.</i>

00:14:29.537 --> 00:14:31.004 position:41% line:5% align:start
I've made friends,

00:14:31.038 --> 00:14:34.875 position:44% line:5% align:start
and I've learned
to use Shinsu a little bit.

00:14:34.908 --> 00:14:36.110 position:24% line:89% align:start
So it's going to be okay.

00:14:36.143 --> 00:14:38.713 position:27% line:89% align:start
Together, we'll climb --

00:14:38.747 --> 00:14:42.149 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can't climb it with you.</i>

00:14:42.182 --> 00:14:45.452 position:27% line:83% align:start
Han: Do you know
what you desire?

00:14:45.486 --> 00:14:47.054 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>In place of you,</i>

00:14:47.087 --> 00:14:51.892 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>the strong, kind-hearted</i>
 <i>and universally beloved Bam...</i>

00:14:51.925 --> 00:14:56.798 position:5% line:83% align:start
We can look at the stars
at the top...t-together.

00:14:56.831 --> 00:14:59.133 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>...I will become a star</i>
 <i>in your place.</i>

00:14:59.166 --> 00:15:00.802 position:24% line:89% align:start
Rachel?

00:15:00.835 --> 00:15:03.170 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm so sorry, Bam.</i>

00:15:07.842 --> 00:15:10.578 position:27% line:83% align:start
Rak:
Hey! Woman turtle!

00:15:16.383 --> 00:15:19.186 position:13% line:83% align:start
Where the hell
is black turtle?

00:15:20.688 --> 00:15:22.824 position:24% line:83% align:start
We were attacked...
by the bull.

00:15:22.857 --> 00:15:24.458 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-What?

00:15:24.491 --> 00:15:27.961 position:21% line:83% align:start
-You're not serious.
-What do you mean? Where's Bam?

00:15:27.995 --> 00:15:30.532 position:13% line:83% align:start
-What happened to Bam? Hey!
-Rachel.

00:15:31.866 --> 00:15:33.835 position:44% line:89% align:start
Congratulations.

00:15:33.868 --> 00:15:36.838 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:15:36.871 --> 00:15:39.541 position:52% line:83% align:start
Everything
went according to plan.

00:15:42.242 --> 00:15:44.077 position:19% line:83% align:start
Lero-Ro: We thoroughly
searched the area,

00:15:44.111 --> 00:15:48.949 position:21% line:83% align:start
but we couldn't find
Bam's body anywhere.

00:15:48.982 --> 00:15:53.120 position:19% line:83% align:start
He must have been eaten
by a fish.

00:15:53.153 --> 00:15:55.322 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's quite unfortunate.

00:15:55.355 --> 00:15:58.325 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Crying ]

00:15:58.358 --> 00:15:59.527 position:55% line:89% align:start
Um, so...

00:15:59.561 --> 00:16:01.863 position:5% line:77% align:start
may I ask the results
of the test?
[ Growls ]

00:16:01.896 --> 00:16:05.700 position:41% line:71% align:start
Right now? Really?
Shut up! I'm actually here
to climb the tower!

00:16:09.369 --> 00:16:13.106 position:13% line:83% align:start
What's everybody's problem?
-Just shut your mouth.

00:16:13.140 --> 00:16:17.110 position:21% line:83% align:start
The test is over now
and every one of you has passed.

00:16:17.144 --> 00:16:19.112 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[ Sighs ]
-[ Growls ]

00:16:19.146 --> 00:16:21.816 position:16% line:83% align:start
I will contact you later
with the next steps.

00:16:21.850 --> 00:16:24.351 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:24.384 --> 00:16:28.121 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ Rak howling ]

00:16:30.991 --> 00:16:32.827 position:38% line:89% align:start
Damn it.

00:16:32.861 --> 00:16:34.829 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ Howling continues
in distance ]

00:16:34.863 --> 00:16:43.003 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:43.036 --> 00:16:44.739 position:5% line:83% align:start
How much of everything
that occurred

00:16:44.772 --> 00:16:47.107 position:19% line:83% align:start
was always
a part of your plan?

00:16:47.140 --> 00:16:50.845 position:7% line:83% align:start
Only the fish hunt
or everything?

00:16:50.879 --> 00:16:53.715 position:50% line:89% align:start
[ Chuckles ]

00:16:53.748 --> 00:16:55.783 position:5% line:89% align:start
How is this amusing?

00:16:55.817 --> 00:16:59.186 position:5% line:83% align:start
What did you do to Rachel?
Tell me!

00:16:59.219 --> 00:17:01.388 position:35% line:89% align:start
I didn't do anything.

00:17:01.421 --> 00:17:04.759 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:17:04.792 --> 00:17:08.563 position:30% line:83% align:start
Every decision she made
was hers.

00:17:08.596 --> 00:17:11.533 position:44% line:83% align:start
I think everyone
in this room owes Bam a favor,

00:17:11.566 --> 00:17:12.634 position:41% line:89% align:start
even if he's gone.

00:17:16.036 --> 00:17:18.573 position:21% line:83% align:start
Favors should always
be returned.

00:17:18.606 --> 00:17:21.208 position:13% line:83% align:start
-What could we do for him?
-What we can do

00:17:21.241 --> 00:17:24.444 position:16% line:83% align:start
is take the woman turtle
to the top of the tower for him.

00:17:24.478 --> 00:17:28.883 position:13% line:83% align:start
Rachel's injury
would make it hard on her own.

00:17:28.917 --> 00:17:31.051 position:61% line:89% align:start
Khun?

00:17:31.084 --> 00:17:34.488 position:13% line:83% align:start
This is wrong. We shouldn't
just accept this.

00:17:34.522 --> 00:17:37.525 position:7% line:83% align:start
These shitty rules constrain us
and make us suffer.

00:17:37.559 --> 00:17:38.960 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Laughs ]

00:17:38.993 --> 00:17:42.830 position:27% line:83% align:start
No. We'll change
the whole tower.

00:17:42.864 --> 00:17:44.799 position:27% line:89% align:start
Let's climb it...

00:17:46.601 --> 00:17:48.770 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[ Laughing hysterically ]
-...with Rachel.

00:17:48.803 --> 00:17:53.106 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:17:53.140 --> 00:17:54.576 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Chuckles ]

00:17:54.609 --> 00:18:02.082 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:02.115 --> 00:18:05.053 position:13% line:83% align:start
-You're quitting your job?
-Yes,

00:18:05.085 --> 00:18:08.388 position:38% line:77% align:start
and they're bringing
in some new blood.
What?

00:18:08.422 --> 00:18:12.225 position:33% line:83% align:start
Which means you're now
out of a job, too.

00:18:12.259 --> 00:18:15.329 position:10% line:83% align:start
That's not fair!
I got dragged into your fight.

00:18:15.362 --> 00:18:17.364 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Want to come with me?
-Huh?

00:18:17.397 --> 00:18:20.702 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm going to climb the tower
in search of the truth.

00:18:20.735 --> 00:18:24.072 position:55% line:83% align:start
Hold on.
What are you saying?

00:18:24.104 --> 00:18:25.873 position:55% line:89% align:start
Lero-Ro.

00:18:25.907 --> 00:18:28.543 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:28.576 --> 00:18:30.110 position:30% line:89% align:start
Han: It's fine.

00:18:30.143 --> 00:18:32.680 position:24% line:83% align:start
Everything has gone
according to plan.

00:18:32.714 --> 00:18:36.684 position:13% line:83% align:start
All the Princesses of Jahad
now believe Bam is dead.

00:18:36.718 --> 00:18:43.524 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:43.558 --> 00:18:46.594 position:35% line:83% align:start
Stars shine anywhere,
especially in the dark.

00:18:46.628 --> 00:18:51.264 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:51.298 --> 00:18:54.869 position:21% line:83% align:start
Let me offer a prayer
for those of you remaining.

00:18:56.738 --> 00:18:59.574 position:7% line:83% align:start
I hope whatever it is you seek
lies at the end

00:18:59.607 --> 00:19:02.777 position:21% line:83% align:start
of the difficult path
you're all about to travel.

00:19:02.810 --> 00:19:04.311 position:7% line:89% align:start
Know that the hand grasping...

00:19:04.344 --> 00:19:08.281 position:5% line:83% align:start
Bam really cared about you more
than anything in this world.

00:19:08.315 --> 00:19:11.318 position:19% line:83% align:start
I pray you can be proud
of the path you've walked.

00:19:11.351 --> 00:19:13.921 position:52% line:77% align:start
Yes, I know.
No, you don't.

00:19:13.955 --> 00:19:15.255 position:66% line:77% align:start
Huh?
If you really knew,

00:19:15.288 --> 00:19:17.391 position:13% line:83% align:start
there's no way
you would still be here.

00:19:17.424 --> 00:19:19.694 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:19.727 --> 00:19:24.065 position:5% line:83% align:start
I so wish I could have met Bam
before you did.

00:19:24.098 --> 00:19:26.134 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Sighs ]

00:19:26.166 --> 00:19:28.736 position:44% line:83% align:start
It's clear to me
that he was well-loved.

00:19:28.770 --> 00:19:35.308 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:35.342 --> 00:19:38.713 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hwa: Even if the two of you
are reunited,

00:19:38.746 --> 00:19:43.818 position:21% line:83% align:start
